# Bill of Materials (BOM) for Drone Build

---

## 1. Airframe

| Item              | Description               | Quantity | Part Number / Link         | Notes                 |
|-------------------|--------------------------|----------|----------------------------|-----------------------|
| Frame Kit         | Carbon fiber or plastic   | 1        |                            | Specify size (e.g., 450mm) |
| Landing Gear      | Compatible with frame     | 1        |                            |                       |
| Vibration Dampers | For camera/gimbal mount   | 4        |                            | Optional              |

---

## 2. Propulsion System

| Item              | Description                  | Quantity | Part Number / Link         | Notes                 |
|-------------------|-----------------------------|----------|----------------------------|-----------------------|
| Brushless Motors  | Specify KV rating           | 4        |                            | One per arm           |
| Electronic Speed Controllers (ESC) | Match motor specs         | 4        |                            |                       |
| Propellers        | Specify size and material    | 4 (2 CW, 2 CCW) |                    | Include spares        |
| Power Distribution Board (PDB) | For ESCs and power lines     | 1        |                            |                       |

---
## 3. Acuators

| Item              | Description                  | Quantity | Part Number / Link         | Notes                 |
|-------------------|-----------------------------|----------|----------------------------|-----------------------|
| Servo's   | Emax ES09MD  | 8 |0102003014| (dual-bearing) specific swash servo for 450 helicopters |

---

## 3. Flight Control & Sensors

| Item                  | Description                | Quantity | Part Number / Link         | Notes                 |
|-----------------------|---------------------------|----------|----------------------------|-----------------------|
| Flight Controller     | (e.g., Pixhawk, Betaflight) | 1      |                            |                       |
| GPS Module            | With compass               | 1        |                            | Optional but recommended |
| IMU/Accelerometer     | Usually built-in           | 1        |                            |                       |
| Barometer             | Usually built-in           | 1        |                            |                       |
| Telemetry Module      | 433MHz/915MHz/2.4GHz       | 1        |                            | Optional              |

---

## 4. Power System

| Item                  | Description                | Quantity | Part Number / Link         | Notes                 |
|-----------------------|---------------------------|----------|----------------------------|-----------------------|
| Battery (LiPo)        | e.g., 4S 5200mAh           | 1-2      |                            | Capacity as needed    |
| Battery Straps        | Velcro or similar          | 2        |                            |                       |
| Battery Charger       | Compatible with battery    | 1        |                            |                       |
| Power Module          | Voltage/current sensor      | 1        |                            | For flight controller |

---

## 5. Radio Control

| Item                  | Description                | Quantity | Part Number / Link         | Notes                 |
|-----------------------|---------------------------|----------|----------------------------|-----------------------|
| RC Transmitter        | 6+ channels                | 1        |                            |                       |
| RC Receiver           | Compatible with transmitter | 1        |                            |                       |
| Antennas              | For receiver/transmitter    | 2        |                            |                       |

---

## 6. Video & Camera (Optional)

| Item                  | Description                | Quantity | Part Number / Link         | Notes                 |
|-----------------------|---------------------------|----------|----------------------------|-----------------------|
| FPV Camera            | For live video             | 1        |                            | Optional              |
| Video Transmitter     | 5.8GHz recommended         | 1        |                            | Optional              |
| Video Receiver        | For ground station         | 1        |                            | Optional              |
| Onboard Camera        | e.g., GoPro, Insta360      | 1        |                            | Optional              |
| Gimbal                | For stabilized footage     | 1        |                            | Optional              |

---

## 7. Cables & Accessories

| Item                  | Description                | Quantity | Part Number / Link         | Notes                 |
|-----------------------|---------------------------|----------|----------------------------|-----------------------|
| Power Cables          | Silicone wire, various gauges | As needed |                        |                       |
| Connectors            | XT60, JST, bullet, etc.    | As needed |                            |                       |
| Zip Ties              | For cable management       | As needed |                            |                       |
| Double-sided Tape     | For mounting electronics   | As needed |                            |                       |
| Heat Shrink Tubing    | For insulation             | As needed |                            |                       |

