## 8. Tools Required

| Tool                  | Description                | Notes                           |
|-----------------------|---------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Soldering Iron        | For wiring                 |                                  |
| Screwdriver Set       | Phillips/Hex               |                                  |
| Wire Strippers/Cutters| For cable preparation      |                                  |
| Multimeter            | For diagnostics            |                                  |
| Propeller Balancer    | For smooth flight          | Optional                        |

