## 9. Miscellaneous

| Item                  | Description                | Quantity | Notes                      |
|-----------------------|---------------------------|----------|----------------------------|
| Spare Propellers      |                           | 2-4      |                            |
| Stickers/Labels       | For marking components     | As needed|                            |
| Documentation         | Manuals, datasheets        | As needed|                            |

